title: New Creator: Divine
body:
Name: Divine 

Socials: 
https://discord.gg/amongusglobal
https://discord.gg/HVchMK7H

Info: Divine is the owner of two very popular gaming Discords. His Among Us Global Discord has 135,000 members and his Divine Customs sever has 37,000 members. Divine plans on using his coin for both servers!

Targeted Use Case: Exclusive roles, gated channels, and giveaways. Tournaments gated with coin and as well pay outs in coin. 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1000

A "Yes" vote would approve Divine as a creator, and provide a $1000 grant.

A "No" vote would reject Divine from the platform.
author: 0xa1e4270381e381E75ef6e4dDa1a27337a4Be0939
